The paper deals with neural networks and their implementation for edge computing, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The focus on extreme quantization and energy efficiency suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of ResNet and VGG architectures suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the computer architecture (cs.AR) sub-category.
